{"tid":2394042,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"保錡沙律拍拖放閃    稱無憂慮顧忌   所有留言一致讚好   指又有夫妻相","createTime":"2021-02-04T02:10:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-05T02:21:47.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"75ac8e822e0efb2d3b7b348767451ff39a9b5dbb","tid":2394042,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T02:10:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/JZM1LqcWvVYCmYPAFmJ6RA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTExOTguNTAxODcyNjU5MTc2MQ--/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/xwNIHYewww3.llsEPNUcRw--~B/aD0xMDAwO3c9ODAxO2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/singtao.com.hk/22a8d545cd38e4cf1bf8fe26dfdbeb58\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FJZM1LqcWvVYCmYPAFmJ6RA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTExOTguNTAxODcyNjU5MTc2MQ--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FxwNIHYewww3.llsEPNUcRw--~B%2FaD0xMDAwO3c9ODAxO2FwcGlkPXl0YWNoeW9u%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fko%2Fsingtao.com.hk%2F22a8d545cd38e4cf1bf8fe26dfdbeb58&h=89e39c8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】組合ERROR成員吳保錡早前被指未與舊愛賴嘉賢（Carrie）分手、就和張沛樂（沙律）拍拖，被不少網民鬧爆，保錡事後表示會重新出發，公開認愛「沙律」的他不時和女友在社交網放閃，近日他就和「沙律」分別在社交網分享拍拖歎下午茶的合照，再度放閃，當日二人雖然有朋友同行，但沙律留言說：「難得可以與朋友相聚去環境優美舒服的地方享受下午茶，沒有憂慮沒有顧忌。」不過今次所有留言都是一致讚好，指他們很襯又有夫妻相。"},{"pid":"c3e9e8f18adaa7545a2e402f26a32035ddc5f651","tid":2394042,"uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T02:13:36.000Z","msg":"唔知做過愛未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71f7973eefe141d42539a34dd1f6d18d83c97358","tid":2394042,"uid":66559,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T02:14:27.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"fc0f02b81c8158106df10550685f04adf0529c83","tid":2394042,"uid":219583,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c3e9e8f18adaa7545a2e402f26a32035ddc5f651","tid":2394042,"ui